Class JobService

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lergin.laborus.api.JobService

  • public class JobService
extends java.lang.Object
    The service to register JobBoni, JobActions and JobAbilities. Is provided by Sponges ServiceManager after the GameConstruction: Sponge.getServiceManager().getRegistration(JobService.class).get().getProvider();
